item.description:
This restaurant is so delicious, we are going there again! Join us for dinner at El Basha Restaurant in Westborough, located just off Rt. 9 on Connector Road. El Basha features a wide range of Mediterranean Cuisine. After dinner, we will be heading a short distance down Rt. 9 for our weekly trivia.

Everyone pays for their own food/drink. If you have trouble finding us, please call Catherine at 774 232 0000. Look forward to seeing you!
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine (see photo) inside ent. If need to, please call 774 232 0000
item.name: Pre-Trivia Dinner at El Basha Restaurant, Westborough
